---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Explorar - DevXtreme">
  <section class="explorar-container">

    <header class="section-header">
      <span class="subtitle reveal">// ACERCA DEL EVENTO</span>
      <h1 class="title reveal delay-1">¿Qué es <span class="highlight neon-title">DevXtreme?</span></h1>
    </header>

    <div class="content-grid">

      <div class="main-text">
        <p class="reveal delay-2">
          DevXtreme 3.0 es la tercera edición de la competencia de programación que reúne a los mejores talentos en desarrollo de software para medirse en retos de algoritmos, lógica y resolución de problemas bajo presión real.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal delay-3">
          Los participantes enfrentarán un conjunto de problemas cuidadosamente diseñados para evaluar eficiencia, creatividad y dominio técnico en un entorno de alta intensidad.
        </p>
        <p class="cta-text reveal delay-4">
          Solo tienes cuatro horas. Cada segundo cuenta. ¿Estás listo para llevar tu código al límite?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-panel">
        <div class="stat-card reveal-zoom" style="--delay: 0.2s; --bar-color: var(--purple)">
          <span class="stat-value">4H</span>
          <span class="stat-label">DE COMPETENCIA</span>
          <div class="stat-bar"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card reveal-zoom" style="--delay: 0.28s; --bar-color: var(--cyan)">
          <span class="stat-value">3.0</span>
          <span class="stat-label">EDICIÓN</span>
          <div class="stat-bar"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card reveal-zoom" style="--delay: 0.36s; --bar-color: var(--mint)">
          <span class="stat-value">N+1</span>
          <span class="stat-label">RETOS TÉCNICOS</span>
          <div class="stat-bar"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card reveal-zoom" style="--delay: 0.44s; --bar-color: var(--magenta)">
          <span class="stat-value">∞</span>
          <span class="stat-label">LÍNEAS DE CÓDIGO</span>
          <div class="stat-bar"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .explorar-container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 20px 60px;
  }

  :global(.home-btn) {
    left: 20px !important;
    top: 120px !important;
    width: 55px !important;
    height: 55px !important;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .section-header { margin-bottom: 50px; }

  .subtitle {
    display: block;
    font-family: monospace;
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--sky-blue), var(--purple), var(--cyan));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  /* ── CONTENT GRID ── */
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .main-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--magenta) !important;
    font-size: 1.05rem !important;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--magenta);
    background: rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.04);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }

  [data-theme="dark"] .cta-text {
    background: rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.08);
  }

  /* ── STATS PANEL ── */
  .stats-panel {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
    padding: 25px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275),
                box-shadow 0.35s ease,
                border-color 0.35s ease,
                background 0.4s ease;
  }

  .stat-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(255,122,0,0.04), transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
  }
  .stat-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    border-color: var(--bar-color);
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-card-title);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .stat-card:hover .stat-value {
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    margin-top: 5px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: color 0.4s ease;
  }

  .stat-bar {
    height: 4px;
    width: 40px;
    margin-top: 15px;
    background: var(--bar-color);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
  }

  .stat-card:hover .stat-bar { width: 70%; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .explorar-container { padding-top: 140px; }

    :global(.home-btn) {
      top: 90px !important;
      width: 45px !important;
      height: 45px !important;
      left: 15px !important;
    }

    .title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .stats-panel { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>